---
---

<section class="hiw" aria-labelledby="hiw-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hiw__card">
      <h2 class="hiw__heading" id="hiw-heading">
        Three phases.<br />One ring.<br />Total clarity.
      </h2>

      <div class="hiw__step">
        <div class="hiw__step-marker">
          <div class="hiw__step-num">01</div>
          <div class="hiw__step-thread"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hiw__step-content">
          <h3 class="hiw__step-title">Start your fast</h3>
          <p class="hiw__step-body">
            Set your eating window once. FastMode does the rest — tracking your fast from there.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hiw__step">
        <div class="hiw__step-marker">
          <div class="hiw__step-num hiw__step-num--featured">02</div>
          <div class="hiw__step-thread"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hiw__step-content">
          <h3 class="hiw__step-title hiw__step-title--featured">Watch your body shift gears</h3>
          <p class="hiw__step-body">
            At 12 hours, you enter Fat Burn. At 16, Peak Fat Burn. Your timer gives you hints — no guessing required.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hiw__step hiw__step--last">
        <div class="hiw__step-marker">
          <div class="hiw__step-num">03</div>
        </div>
        <div class="hiw__step-content">
          <h3 class="hiw__step-title">Build the habit</h3>
          <p class="hiw__step-body">
            Your streak grows every day you complete a fast. Feeling sick? Streak Freeze has your back. No all-or-nothing pressure.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hiw {
    padding: 0 0 16px;
  }

  .hiw__card {
    background: #40AB51;
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 52px 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .hiw__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 34px;
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    text-align: center;
    color: #F7EFE9;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .hiw__step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
    padding-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .hiw__step--last {
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .hiw__step-marker {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    align-self: stretch;
  }

  .hiw__step-num {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1.5px solid #E5E5E5;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: white;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .hiw__step-num--featured {
    background: white;
    border-color: #40AB51;
    color: #4CAF7D;
  }

  .hiw__step-thread {
    width: 1.5px;
    flex: 1;
    min-height: 28px;
    margin-top: 6px;
    background: #E5E5E5;
  }

  .hiw__step-content {
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  .hiw__step-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: #F7EFE9;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .hiw__step-title--featured {
    font-size: 22px;
  }

  .hiw__step-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #F7EFE9;
  }
</style>
